    <item>
      <title>DNF Automatic İle Paketleri Otomatik Güncelleyin</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/tr/yazilar/dnf-automatic/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 May 2022 00:00:00 +0300</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/tr/yazilar/dnf-automatic/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DNF Automatic&lt;/strong&gt; ile Fedora ve RHEL gibi DNF paket yöneticisine sahip GNU/Linux dağıtımlarındaki güncelleme işlemlerini otomatikleştirmeniz mümkün.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;dnf-automatici-yükleyin&#34;&gt;DNF Automatic&amp;rsquo;i Yükleyin&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bunun için kullandığınız terminale aşağıdaki kodu yazın ve yüklemeyi onaylayarak, kurulumu tamamlayın:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;
&lt;table style=&#34;border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&#34;vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo dnf install dnf-automatic
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;dnf-automatici-yapılandırın&#34;&gt;DNF Automatic&amp;rsquo;i Yapılandırın&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Otomatik güncellemeleri yapılandırmak için iki yöntem mevcut:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;etcdnfautomaticconf-dosyasını-düzenleyin&#34;&gt;/etc/dnf/automatic.conf Dosyasını Düzenleyin&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bu dosya, varsayılan yapılandırma dosyasıdır. Paketi yüklediğinizde oluşturulacaktır. Herhangi bir metin editörü ile dosyayı açın:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;
&lt;table style=&#34;border-spacing:0;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&#34;vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;white-space:pre;-webkit-user-select:none;user-select:none;margin-right:0.4em;padding:0 0.4em 0 0.4em;color:#7f7f7f&#34;&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td style=&#34;vertical-align:top;padding:0;margin:0;border:0;;width:100%&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#282a36;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;sudo vim /etc/dnf/automatic.conf
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Yukarıdaki değerler, varsayılandır.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
